The file  SERUS221.ZIP  contains 6 files:

   README          -- This file.

   SERIOUS.SYS     -- The  SERIOUS  device driver.

   SERIOUS.DOC     -- Users guide for  SERIOUS .

   SERFACE.C       -- C interface routines for  SERIOUS .

   SERFACE.H       -- Include file for  serface.c .

   SERDEMO.C       -- A dumb terminal, to be linked with
                      the routines of  serface.c .

   This is version  2.21  of  SERIOUS  , and is implemented as a  DOS
   installable device driver.



